DISCLAIMER FOR EMAIL SECURITY APPLICATION:

This spam detection software is intended for educational and research purposes.
When implementing this technology in production email systems:

1. PRIVACY: Ensure compliance with data protection regulations (GDPR, CCPA)
2. TRANSPARENCY: Inform users about automated email classification
3. ACCURACY: Regular monitoring and updates to maintain detection quality
4. ETHICS: Respect user privacy and communication rights
5. SECURITY: Implement proper data handling and storage practices

The author is not responsible for any misuse of this technology or any legal
issues arising from its implementation in email systems. Users are advised
to consult with legal and cybersecurity professionals before deploying in
production environments.

